  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Entering Authorizations</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio4804c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Entering Authorizations</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\"> When entering the payment parameters, you can restrict the authorization to change the payment parameters to a limited number of users. Proceed as follows: </p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose\n<span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Authorized users</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">.</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the SAP user names of the users to whom you are giving authorization to change the payment parameters.</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">To continue, choose\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Continue</span>\n.\n</p></li></ol>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
